      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Nemorino</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ef/NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg/330px-NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ef/NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg/500px-NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ef/NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg/960px-NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:NemorinoLelisirDamore.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Nemorino enjoys the alleged effect of the love potion <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Nemorino</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant, free <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Christian Günther</a>, also supporting the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> and first released in September 2016 under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPLv3</a> license. Nemorino's <a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">board representation</a> and <a href=\"/Encoding_Moves\" title=\"Encoding Moves\">move structure</a> are taken from <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Nemorino supports <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a> based on <a href=\"/Basil_Falcinelli\" title=\"Basil Falcinelli\">Basil Falcinelli's</a> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom API</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, applies a very <a href=\"/Parallel_Search#Lazy\" title=\"Parallel Search\">lazy parallel search</a>, and is able to play <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Etymology\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Etymology</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2016_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etymology\">Etymology</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Etymology\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Nemorino is named after the a character of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaetano_Donizetti\">Gaetano Donizetti's</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comic_opera\">comic opera</a><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%27elisir_d%27amore\">L'elisir d'amore</a>, premiered on May 12, 1832 at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teatro_Lirico_(Milan)\">Teatro alla Canobbiana</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milan\">Milan</a>. Nemorino, a poor peasant, in love with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adina\">Adina</a>, asks <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quackery\">quack doctor</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dulcamara\">Dulcamara</a> for <a href=\"/Tristram\" title=\"Tristram\">Isolde's</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Love_potion\">love potion</a>, who sells him a bottle of cheap <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bordeaux_wine\">Bordeaux wine</a> instead ...\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Copy-Make\" title=\"Copy-Make\">Copy/Make</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a> with <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a> / <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Mate_Distance_Pruning\" title=\"Mate Distance Pruning\">Mate Distance Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Recapture_Extensions\" title=\"Recapture Extensions\">Recapture Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Hash_Move\" title=\"Hash Move\">Hash Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/PV-Move\" title=\"PV-Move\">PV-Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic#CMHist\" title=\"History Heuristic\">Followup History Heuristic</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> (Nemorino 6) <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Endgame\" title=\"Endgame\">Endgame Knowledge</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Category:Fiction\" title=\"Category:Fiction\">Fiction</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Nemo\" title=\"Nemo\">Nemo</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Peasant\" title=\"Peasant\">Peasant</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristram\" title=\"Tristram\">Tristram</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016_...\">2016 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 2016 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61507\">Nemorino - new engine</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Christian Günther</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 23, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62845\">Nemorino 2.0</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Christian Günther</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2017 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63450\">Nemorino 2.0a is available ...</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 15, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64336\">Nemorino 3</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Christian Günther</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65447&amp;start=18\">Re: TCEC 10</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Christian Günther</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_10\" title=\"TCEC Season 10\">TCEC Season 10</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66086\">Nemorino 4</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Christian Günther</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68046&amp;p=769135\">Nemorino 5</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Florentino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 22, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75241\">Nemorino 6 (NNUE)</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Florentino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77503&amp;start=55\">Re: will Tcec allow Stockfish with a Leela net to play?</a> by <a href=\"/Connor_McMonigle\" title=\"Connor McMonigle\">Connor McMonigle</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/christian_g_nther/nemorino\">Christian Günther / Nemorino — Bitbucket</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerchess.org.uk/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Nemorino&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Nemorino</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/40</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%27elisir_d%27amore\">L'elisir d'amore from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Una_furtiva_lagrima\">Una furtiva lagrima from Wikipedia</a>\t</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:The_Searchers\" title=\"Category:The Searchers\">The Searchers</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Love_Potion_No._9_(song)\">Love potion number 9</a> (1963), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/7rXhXLsNJL8?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nemorino&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Nemorino enjoys the alleged effect of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Love_potion\">love potion</a>, surrounded by the village girls and jealously Adina in the background,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brown_Opera_Productions\">Brown Opera Productions</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brown_University\">Brown University</a>, Spring 2009 show <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%27elisir_d%27amore\">L'elisir d'amore</a>, Image by Joeforemperor, April 07, 2009, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/christian_g_nther/nemorino/overview\">Christian Günther / Nemorino — Bitbucket</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/Fathom\">GitHub - basil00/Fathom: Syzygy TB probe tool</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75241\">Nemorino 6 (NNUE)</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_G%C3%BCnther&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Günther (page does not exist)\">Florentino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 2020</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301153017\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.614 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 120/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 238/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:3828-0!canonical and timestamp 20260